These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, january, april, september
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, lily, tulip, azalea
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, scientific, mystery, crime
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, horse, rat
 1. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person who growspoppy is on the left or right of the person who growslily##3
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person watching scientific movies is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the rat and the person who growsazalea##2
10. the person who's birthday is in june is the owner of the rat##1
11. the person who growstulip is the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Birthday          | april  | june    | september    | january   |
| Flower   | lily     | poppy   | tulip       | azalea    |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | time-travel | crime    | mystery |
| Pet           | hamster | rat       | chinchilla | horse     |

