.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, eggplant, kale, peas
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, marigold, lily, daffodil
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, dancer, project-manager, accountant
City: boston, venice, paris, berlin
 1. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
 2. the dancer is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 3. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 4. the person eating eggplant is the doctor##1
 5. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the doctor is on the left or right of the project-manager##3
 7. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating kale##1
 8. the accountant is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
 9. the project-manager is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
11. the project-manager is the person who growslily##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Food          | carrot  | eggplant    | kale     | peas       |
| Flower         | lily | daffodil | azalea   | marigold |
| Job   | project-manager | doctor   | dancer   | accountant    |
| City         | paris | berlin  | boston | venice   |

