.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-4::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, june, october
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, marigold, poppy, daffodil
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, disaster, martial-arts, romance
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, ice-hockey, parkour, surfing
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
 3. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
 4. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is surfing##1
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the person who growsdaffodil##3
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
11. the person who's birthday is in june is the person who growsdaffodil##1
12. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left or right of the person who growssunflower##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | october       | june   | january   | march   |
| Flower       | marigold        | daffodil | sunflower    | poppy       |
| Movie-Genre      | romance | disaster    | martial-arts  | musical |
| Sport      | ice-hockey  | parkour  | cycling | surfing    |

