.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-5::.
City: hannover, new-york, paris, edinburgh
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, futuristic, tower
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, librarian, manager, musician
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, juice, lemonade, fanta
 1. the person drinking juice is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the futuristic house is between the person drinking cola and the person traveling to edinburgh##2
 3. the manager is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 4. the librarian is the person traveling to hannover##1
 5. the bartender is on the left or right of the librarian##3
 6. the townhouse house is in an even position##4
 7. the person traveling to new-york is the bartender##1
 8. the futuristic house is the librarian##1
 9. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
10. the librarian is on the right of the tower house##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
12. the tower house is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2       |       3       |     4     |
| City    | paris    | edinburgh      | hannover          | new-york    |
| House   | gothic-revival | tower       | futuristic | townhouse |
| Job     | musician     | manager      | librarian     | bartender |
| Beverage   | juice   | fanta | lemonade        | cola   |

