There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, german, indian
 1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 4. the colonial house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 5. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is between the german and the person who's birthday is in january##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person watching superhero movies##1
 8. the palace house is the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the colombian is on the far right##1
10. the canadian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| House      | colonial  | palace    | gothic-revival       | townhouse       |
| Movie-Genre          | epic    | superhero | adventure | sports     |
| Birthday   | october | november        | july    | january   |
| Nationality   | canadian  | german      | indian    | colombian |

