The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, board-games, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, skateboard, subway, trike
 1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 2. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 3. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the person who growszinnia##3
 5. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
 9. the fan of funk is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the far right##1
11. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
12. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4      |
