.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, dancing, puzzles, traveling
4 different games are played: backgammon, monopoly, whist, domino
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daffodil, begonia, balloon-flower, aconite
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, peas, corn, kiwi
 1. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating raspberry is between the person eating kiwi and the person eating corn##2
 3. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is dancing##3
 7. the person eating corn is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 8. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is between the person who growsdaffodil and the person playing monopoly##2
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
11. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an even position##4
12. the person playing backgammon is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby         | dancing  | puzzles    | chess    | traveling |
| Game   | whist   | backgammon       | monopoly  | domino    |
| Flower   | daffodil | begonia | balloon-flower | aconite   |
| Food           | corn    | raspberry        | kiwi   | peas    |

