The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, fishing, woodworking, photography
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, jazz
House: colonial, palace, gothic-revival, townhouse
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 2. the gothic-revival house is in an even position##4
 3. the fan of folk is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the palace house##2
 4. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
 6. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
 8. the townhouse house is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 9. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
11. the person traveling to london is on the far left or far right##3
12. the fan of house is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
13. the fan of indie is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| City          | london     | edinburgh      | marseilles  | paris        |
| Hobby   | fishing     | woodworking | gardening | photography      |
| Music-Genre   | house      | folk        | jazz        | indie        |
| House         | townhouse | colonial    | palace      | gothic-revival |

