.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-10::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, cranberry, grapefruit, pomegranate
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, musician, police-officer, social-worker
4 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, snake, rabbit
4 different games are played: whist, snooker, mah-jongg, chess
 1. the person playing whist is on the left or right of the person playing snooker##3
 2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person playing whist##1
 3. the musician is between the person playing chess and the person playing whist##2
 4. the person playing chess is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the person playing chess is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the owner of the snake is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person eating cranberry is on the far right##1
 8. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the social-worker is on the left of the musician##1
10. the dancer is in an even position##4
11. the owner of the dog is the person eating eggplant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |       3        |       4       |
| Food      | grapefruit      | pomegranate      | eggplant           | cranberry |
| Job           | social-worker | musician | police-officer | dancer        |
| Pet   | snake      | rabbit  | dog          | hedgehog      |
| Game         | chess       | mah-jongg    | whist       | snooker       |

