There are 4 different nationalities: australian, polish, argentine, russian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, iced-tea, juice
 1. the russian is in an odd position##4
 2. the russian is on the left or right of the person eating kiwi##3
 3. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the australian##3
 4. the person drinking juice is between the baccarat-smoker and the argentine##2
 5. the person eating plum is the fonseca-smoker##1
 6. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
 7. the person eating mango is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
 9. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking water is the dunhill-smoker##1
11. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
12. the australian is on the left or right of the polish##3
13. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food    | raspberry    | kiwi        | plum   | mango      |
| Cigar   | cain  | baccarat     | fonseca | dunhill  |
