.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-19::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, pony, guinea-pig, goat
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, photography, singing, video-games
City: rome, venice, boston, marseilles
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, doctor, firefighter, security-guard
 1. the doctor is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 2. the security-guard is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 3. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is in an even position##4
 5. the analyst is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
 8. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is card-games##3
10. the firefighter is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person traveling to marseilles is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3      |      4      |
| Pet      | guinea-pig       | pony | dog        | goat        |
| Hobby         | video-games | singing       | card-games | photography |
| City   | marseilles     | venice        | rome    | boston      |
| Job         | doctor     | firefighter    | security-guard | analyst   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-20::.
City: nizza, boston, hamburg, san-francisco
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, water, almond-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, photography, magic-tricks, camping
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, helicopter, skateboard
 1. the person traveling to san-francisco is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
 4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
 5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person traveling to boston is the person who's hobby is photography##1
 7. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is gardening##3
10. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
12. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| City   | boston      | nizza | san-francisco     | hamburg        |
| Beverage   | water | almond-milk  | sprite     | juice |
| Hobby         | photography    | gardening | magic-tricks      | camping |
| Transport     | skateboard | car     | helicopter | bike       |

 